  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Game</h2><br>Arrowstorm Ascendant is a rogue-like shoot 'em up based on \"Seraph's Last Stand\" and \"Vampire Survivors\". Defeat hordes of dragons and wyverns with your outstanding archery skills. With each new wave you fight more enemies with more power, while also selecting one new upgrade. Create the most interesting, powerful or game breaking build and try to reach the top of the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everytime you restart you lose your previous powerups, but you can acquire gold coins while playing to buy new upgrades:<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can choose 4 green cards and 4 blue cards after each wave. Find the best build possible and reach the highest level you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 different cards with green, red or blue upgrades. Create your build using a combination of 4 blue and 4 green cards (red card are infinite).<br><br></li><li> 11 different skins to choose from, with each skin having its own advantage.<br><br></li><li> A leaderboard system divided by score, enemies defeated and coins obtained.<br><br></li><li> A boss fight once you reach a certain number of waves.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Game</h2><br>Arrowstorm Ascendant is a rogue-like shoot 'em up based on \"Seraph's Last Stand\" and \"Vampire Survivors\". Defeat hordes of dragons and wyverns with your outstanding archery skills. With each new wave you fight more enemies with more power, while also selecting one new upgrade. Create the most interesting, powerful or game breaking build and try to reach the top of the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/5f36436aac3aeada03b28128feb23666.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everytime you restart you lose your previous powerups, but you can acquire gold coins while playing to buy new upgrades:<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/0fd333e9c27f84860de03bcef537c137.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can choose 4 green cards and 4 blue cards after each wave. Find the best build possible and reach the highest level you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.poster.avif?t=1707912076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.webm?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785750/extras/74117f25ea2fd5de1ff23cd780875b5b.mp4?t=1707912076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 different cards with green, red or blue upgrades. Create your build using a combination of 4 blue and 4 green cards (red card are infinite).<br><br></li><li> 11 different skins to choose from, with each skin having its own advantage.<br><br></li><li> A leaderboard system divided by score, enemies defeated and coins obtained.<br><br></li><li> A boss fight once you reach a certain number of waves.</li></ul>",
